data.description:
Caviness & Cates’ Bladen - This home features both a formal dining room with coffered ceiling and wainscoting detail and formal flex room. Hardwood flooring throughout the first floor living spaces.
Great room with corner gas fireplace. Kitchen and breakfast area with granite counter tops, tile back splash stainless microwave, dishwasher, smooth top range, double ovens and side-by-side refrigerator, island and access to covered porch. Master Suite on the first floor with beautiful tray ceiling, walk-in closet, tile flooring in bathroom, his and hers sinks with cultured marble vanity, garden tub and separate shower with tile surroundings. Utility room with built-in bench, coat hooks and cubbies. 2 additional bedrooms on first floor with walk-in closets. Second floor with 2 additional bedrooms, bonus media room and full bathroom. 2 car garage; security system. Low maintenance vinyl siding with stone façade, stone skirt, shake accents, dimensional shingles and Dutch hips. An Energy Plus Certified home.
Home is located in the Jack Britt school district. Westhaven offers a  well lit community park with playground and grill pits.
